Pole: Rinny, what's wrong? It seems like there was a terrible
battle...
Pole: Damn it...! It must be their doing. Bastards...

They're all incredibly strong. They can't possibly be dead.

lie that they're dead!
Rinny: Yes, heroes... They were desperately protecting you all...
Rinny: But they're all dead... I'm sorry.
Lilim: No... I don't want to believe it.
Rinny: Pray for them. For the sake of the heroes...
Lilim: Goodbye... Lima... Wendy... my heroes...
Lilim: Everyone's dead... What's going to happen to this town now...?

Rinny: From now on... this town will be protected by the Knights of
Messiah.

Rinny: Don't worry. This town and Jupiterino will be protected by the
Knights of Messiah, as the commander of Moduna has said.
Lilim: Yes...! The Knights of Messiah will save our country!
A letter arrived at the village of Sheena.

The contents of the letter left Becky and the others unable to hide
their surprise.
